rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, goodness! I'm so glad you made it out alive![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0020
rows.name: I... I wasn't sure what to do, how to help...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0030
rows.name: So seeing you here... It's truly a blessing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0040
rows.name: Ah! I guess this is no time to get sentimental.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0050
rows.name: Okay...be brave. This is for our future![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33590100_MSG0060
rows.name: I'll fight... I'll fight with all I have![ST:wait ]
